    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hi @synonymous1984, the syntax should be:\r\n\r\n```js\r\nme.search.addWidget(\r\n  instantsearch.widgets.currentRefinedValues({\r\n    container: '#currentRefinedValues',\r\n    clearAll: 'after',\r\n    cssClasses: {\r\n      root: 'xxx',\r\n      body: 'bodytest',\r\n      clearAll: 'clearAllTest',\r\n      item: 'filter--active'\r\n    },\r\n    templates: {\r\n      header: '<h1>test</h1>'\r\n    },\r\n  })\r\n);\r\n```\r\n\r\nDid the documentation somehow was misleading? How could we improve it?",
