    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Another suggestion for the documentation: template.item does not name the variable which can be used. So how can the item data be shown? itemName, itemCount?\r\n\r\n```\r\nme.search.addWidget(\r\n            instantsearch.widgets.currentRefinedValues({\r\n                container: '#currentRefinedValues',\r\n                clearAll: 'after',\r\n                cssClasses: {\r\n                    clearAll: 'clear-all',\r\n                    item: 'filter--active'\r\n                },\r\n                templates: {\r\n                    header: '<div class=\"shop-sites--headline navigation--headline\">Aktive Filter</div>',\r\n                    item: '<span class=\"filter--active-icon\"></span>'\r\n                },\r\n            })\r\n        );\r\n```\r\n\r\n",
